snippet.title: Fe Official Gamescom Trailer
snippet.description:
Climb, glide and dig your way through a dark Nordic forest and explore its living, breathing ecosystem filled with secrets, side quests and mystical creatures.

Discover More: http://x.ea.com/34268

Become Fe and discover a world that you will never want to leave.
Subscribe for more upcoming EA Originals Trailers: https://www.youtube.com/user/EA.

Fe will be available as digital version only on PlayStation 4, Xbox One, PC via Origin and Nintendo Switch. You can learn more about Zoink Games here: http://www.zoinkgames.com/.

Coming Early 2018, across all platforms.

“Dirty Paws”
Performed by Of Monsters and Men
Written by Arni Gudjonsson, Nanna Hilmarsdottir and Ragnar Thorhallsson  
Published by Sony/ATV Songs LLC
Recording courtesy of Republic Records
